title: Add hDOGEN-LOOT LP (1x Rewards) to Harmony Farms
body:
Add hDOGEN-LOOT (1x Rewards or higher) LOOT-LP to Dogen.finance Harmony LP Farms!

Lootswap is a Harmony LP Farm that is currently doing an activity called GUILDS. They are looking for new Harmony tokens to start 3 GUILDS on their platform. Dogen.finance is new to the Harmony LP Farms and can pick up on this steam.

I have high confidence in the Lootswap and Dogen.finance Teams and I'd like to see them thrive together!

Let's stake hDOGEN-LOOT LOOT-LP Tokens to earn hDOGEN on Dogen.finance!

Dogen.finance TG: t.me/dogenfinance
Lootswap TG: t.me/lootswap
author: 0x8bBEf539C1eD386BAc9dbD50b53aDC4C58a028FC
